  <brief_title>Study Evaluating the Safety of MOA-728 Administered Orally to Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Ascending Multiple Dose Study of the Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of MOA-728 Administered Orally to Healthy Subjects</official_title>
