  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is the first multiple-dose experience in humans with MOA-728 in an oral formulation.
      This study will provide an assessment of the safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics (PK)
      of MOA-728 following administration of ascending multiple oral doses to healthy subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
